# /etc/portage/package.accept_keywords — per-package keyword overrides
#
# Format: cat/pkg  ~arch   (or ** for all keywords)
#         =cat/pkg-1.2  ~amd64
#
# This can also be a directory containing multiple files.
# portage-ng reads it and maps entries into preference:local_accept_keywords/1
# (per-package keyword acceptance).
#
# See: https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki//etc/portage/package.accept_keywords
